      h2(data-device-preview="../docs-demos/core/timeline-horizontal.html") Horizontal Timeline
      p Horizontal Timeline has the same layout as Vertical but witha addional `timeline-horizontal` class on main `timeline` element.
      p We can also control columns per view in timeline by using <a href="grid.html">Layout Grid</a> columns' classes like `col-33` and `tablet-20` (to define column width for large tablet screens).
      :code(lang="html")
